            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1641298205063-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1641298205063-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the sauce is thickening, add the <strong>Tenderstem broccoli</strong> to a separate pot, cover them with <strong>boiled water</strong> (just enough to cover them) and season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 3-4 min or until tender</p><p>Once cooked, drain the <strong>Tenderstem broccoli </strong>and return it to the pot</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Tenderstem-boiled-1641905607322-x200.jpg",
