            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Tenderstem-boiled-1641905607322-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>single soya </strong>and a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>to the<strong> drained</strong> <strong>potatoes</strong></p><p>Crush the potatoes lightly with a masher or the back of a fork – these are your <strong>crushed potatoes</strong></p><p>Tip: Don't press too hard, you only want to crush them!</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
