      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>pork loin steaks</strong> over the <strong>dairy-free</strong> <strong>peppercorn sauce</strong> with the <strong>crushed potatoes</strong> and <strong>Tenderstem broccoli</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
